# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used with a site-packages/ directory, it is often ignored.
#   Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is generally tracked, but not virtualenvs
